        "### Diagnostics\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "Maybe do a simulation?\n",
        "(individual level diagnostics)\n",
        "Plot of filtered vs smoothed vs observation data\n",
        "Masking, filtered/smoothed performance with RMSE.\n",
        "How much masking causes how much RMSE? \n",
        "(plot masked fraction vs hourly RMSE)\n",
        "Masking random hours, vs whole days?\n",
        "Divergence for people with contiguous missingness, vs spotty missingness\n",
        "\n",
        "[Plot of the three participants' residuals vs missingness, with color-coded by participant, with trend line (potentially a single trendline for each person, and separate trend lines for each person)]"
      ],
